Author: Renlywinsthethrone
Text: Yuge mood. I keep trying to set this sort of stuff as "rewards" for my ittermittent goal weights ("at gw1 you can talk to A Boy™, and at gw2 you can go to A Store™, and at gw3 you can hug someone" etc.) but then when I get there I still feel to gross so I push it all back and I'm probably never gonna do anything until I get to my ugw and the way this is going I'm seriously doubting I'll be able to do anything then either
